reviews.reviewText: Recently, I acquired a phone case that has surpassed all expectations. This case acts as a protective stronghold for my device, combining robust defense with a stylish exterior.The build quality is exceptional, providing a secure grip and instilling confidence in its ability to shield my phone from everyday mishaps. Raised edges around the screen and camera enhance protection, ensuring vulnerable areas remain safe.The design strikes a balance between sleek modernity and functionality. It not only safeguards my phone but also adds a touch of sophistication. Precise cutouts allow easy access to ports and buttons without necessitating case removal.Installation is seamless, and the case's slim profile avoids unnecessary bulk. A resounding recommendation from a satisfied user!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect - even wirelessly charges
reviews.reviewText: This is probably the best case for the money I've ever spent on any case. You get a very thickish case, multiple color options, a screen protector and a lens protector. Depsite the firm protection of the case the button covers are actually very soft and easily click able.I was also able to test the wireless charging on multiple different styles including one that I installed under a office desk. It's one where you lay the phone down on the desk and the charger is under the wood. Even with the thickness of this case it was able to fully wirelessly fast charge.I'm impressed.

reviews.reviewTitle: Excellent value, well made, nice and tough.
reviews.reviewText: I actually did not realize that this came with a camera lens protector and a tempered glass screen protector. I'm not a big fan of screen protectors and usually instead opt to just do my best not to scratch up my screen. Normally I find the protectors difficult to install straight and inevitably trap dust or dirt underneath and choose to just rip it off.Imagine my surprise when, after randomly deciding to try this one anyway, on my second attempt with it I got it perfectly straight and with hardly a spec of dust trapped and not one air bubble. Perfect!I tried the camera lens protector but I hated how it looked and instead opted to remove it. It adhered well though. I'm not worried though due to the cameras being recessed in the case.As for the case itself, it's nice to have a case for the first time in a while without painful sharp edges around the charge port where the phone rests on my finger when in use. The case has lots of texture, is sufficiently grippy and adds much needed bulk. Speaker holes are not obstructed, signal is not impeded at all, and charge port has a nice wide opening and none of my USB c cables failed to fit. Buttons are well moulded and don't add any resistance or squishiness to button presses. Case is both easy enough to install and remove but perfectly snug to the phone when installed.All in all, a fantastic package that only costed me $14.94 Canadian after taxes were applied. This was a rock solid purchase.
